Package: byzanz
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Small screencast creator
 Byzanz is an applet allowing you to record your current desktop or parts of it
 to an animated GIF, Ogg Theora or Flash. This is especially useful for
 publishing on the web.
 .
 Byzanz also allows recording of audio, when the output format supports it.
